message: Added information related to reward-based fundraising including the methods in which it takes place and a list of some prominent platforms that are used with it.
Added information about BSA fundraising to coincide with GSA fundraising.

I included some additional information related to how different organizations utilize product fundraising services and some of the services that are currently being used. There was also an explanation to the influence of electronic commerce on product fundraising.
Added information regarding the applications and implications of water bars of environments.
Added information regarding the market system of sod.
I altered some minor grammatical errors and changed the information regarding Stilwell’s agriculture.
